01_total_count.description: Simple full table count - baseline measurement
01_total_count.query: SELECT COUNT(*) as total FROM images_analytical

02_gender_distribution.description: Gender breakdown with grouping - demographic analysis
02_gender_distribution.query: SELECT gender, COUNT(*) as count FROM images_analytical WHERE gender != '' GROUP BY gender ORDER BY count DESC

03_ethnicity_breakdown.query: SELECT SUM(ethnicity_white) as white, SUM(ethnicity_black) as black, SUM(ethnicity_asian) as asian, SUM(ethnicity_hispanic) as hispanic, SUM(ethnicity_middle_eastern) as middle_eastern, SUM(ethnicity_mixed) as mixed FROM images_analytical

04_top_countries.query: SELECT country_code, COUNT(*) as count FROM images_analytical WHERE country_code != '' GROUP BY country_code ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 15

05_face_presence_filter.query: SELECT COUNT(*) as faces FROM images_analytical WHERE has_face = 1

06_gender_by_region.query: SELECT region, gender, COUNT(*) as count FROM images_analytical WHERE region != '' AND gender != '' GROUP BY region, gender ORDER BY region, count DESC

07_topic_distribution.query: SELECT topic_id_1, COUNT(*) as count FROM images_analytical WHERE topic_id_1 > 0 GROUP BY topic_id_1 ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 20

08_body_pose_clusters.query: SELECT body_pose_cluster_512, COUNT(*) as count FROM images_analytical WHERE body_pose_cluster_512 > 0 GROUP BY body_pose_cluster_512 ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 20

09_multi_filter.description: Multi-condition filter using ordering key prefix
09_multi_filter.query: SELECT COUNT(*) as count FROM images_analytical WHERE has_face = 1 AND has_body = 1 AND detection_top_class_id > 0

10_site_demographics.description: Cross-tabulation - demographics by stock photo site
10_site_demographics.query: SELECT site_name, gender, COUNT(*) as count FROM images_analytical WHERE site_name != '' GROUP BY site_name, gender ORDER BY site_name, count DESC
